  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase II clinical trial, open-label, randomized, two arms, multicentre (possibly
      multinational). Academic, investigator initiated.

      To assess the activity of bevacizumab (AvastinTM) in combination with capecitabine (XelodaTM)
      and radiation therapy with or without oxaliplatin (EloxatinTM) in the pre-operative treatment
      of locally advanced rectal cancer, followed by TME (total mesorectal excision).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
